headline: Is Interactive Brokers (IBKR) a Buy as Wall Street Analysts Look Optimistic?
summary: Based on the average brokerage recommendation (ABR), Interactive Brokers (IBKR) should be added to one's portfolio. Wall Street analysts' overly optimistic recommendations cast doubt on the effectiveness of this highly sought-after metric. So, is the stock worth buying?

headline: Interactive Brokers Launches Zero-Commission US Stock Trading in Singapore
summary: GREENWICH, Conn., August 13, 2025--Interactive Brokers (Nasdaq: IBKR) today announced the launch of its IBKR Lite pricing plan in Singapore.
